http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gap_Inc.\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Ms. Cynthia (Carrion) has been helping me.\", \"from\": 2026, \"to\": 2069, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2031, \"end\": 2038, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cynthia_Lennon\", \"score\": 0.9998084024011097, \"rank\": 0.0001916343038639756, \"text\": \"Cynthia\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cynthia_Lennon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cynthia_Lennon\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I promised that I will still do all the deliverables [of existing contracts].\\\"\", \"from\": 2070, \"to\": 2148, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Yulo said that by independently managing his career, he hopes to put more boundaries between his gymnastics and personal life.\", \"from\": 2150, \"to\": 2276, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My [personal] relationship is out of gymnastics,\\\" Yulo said.\", \"from\": 2278, \"to\": 2339, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If it's in any way connected, I perform with a better well-being.\", \"from\": 2340, \"to\": 2406, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have a better mindset.\", \"from\": 2407, \"to\": 2431, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Win or lose, I am grateful.\\\"\", \"from\": 2432, \"to\": 2460, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"With my partner, I learned to grow.\", \"from\": 2462, \"to\": 2498, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Before, all I know is gymnastics.\", \"from\": 2499, \"to\": 2532, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But when it comes to myself, I do not know much.\", \"from\": 2533, \"to\": 2581, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She helped me grow.\\\"\", \"from\": 2582, \"to\": 2602, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Yulo still remains grateful to Kugimiya as their team-up resulted in two world championships in floor exercise and vault, and a huge haul of gold medals from the World Cup Series, the Southeast Asian Games, and the Asian Artistic Gymnastics Championships.\", \"from\": 2604, \"to\": 2859, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2788, \"end\": 2809, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southeast_Asian_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999999815827, \"rank\": 1.8189902798446186e-11, \"text\": \"Southeast Asian Games\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southeast_Asian_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southeast_Asian_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"A thank you would not be enough,\\\" Yulo said of his former Japanese coach.\", \"from\": 2861, \"to\": 2935, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2920, \"end\": 2928, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\", \"score\": 0.9987295597974813, \"rank\": 0.0006850685717899989, \"text\": \"Japanese\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Isa sa bumuo nang pagkatao ko, sinuportahan ako sa pangarap ko(He's of those who helped me become who I am now and supported my dream).\\\"\", \"from\": 2936, \"to\": 3073, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"-Rappler.com  How does this make you feel?\", \"from\": 3074, \"to\": 3116, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"follow us\", \"from\": 3118, \"to\": 3127, \"entities\": []}]}"